{"tid":2223341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過 “疫情下”/“疫情前” 呢類term好似用撚錯哂疫情呢個詞語","createTime":"2020-09-29T17:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T21:52:41.000Z","uid":366401,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cce2404568e843324fc1ff71ada7d008b58e304a","tid":2223341,"uid":366401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"你話疫情嚴重 ok冇問題<br />\n但疫情本身呢隻字係中性 係valuate疫症嘅現狀<br />\n乜撚嘢叫 &ldquo;疫情下&rdquo; &ldquo;因為疫情&rdquo; &ldquo;有/冇疫情&rdquo;<br />\n個字本身中性 你咁講 咪即係冇講到究竟係正定負面情況<br />\n聽到打冷震 好撚好撚怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得講做 疫症下都仲好啲"},{"pid":"f67d5f2040862e9469e9b57a69cfb881905f2df4","tid":2223341,"uid":366401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:55:01.000Z","msg":"我舉個例啦<br />\n你會唔會話因為我今日心情所以我屌你老母<br />\n或者因為溫度所以我著少咗衫<br />\n你會講 今日心情好曳；今日好凍<br />\n正如咩因為疫情 聽落好撚梗耳 但你講疫情反覆/嚴重反而語意仲更加express到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02eb9acd450f8e184b6d8d5072f11d5d07c9ce2a","tid":2223341,"uid":366401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:56:24.000Z","msg":"期待有人入嚟同我呢個鑽研文法嘅on吹吓水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3682de10c3a554e0a084fff547de81d8bf5b9d","tid":2223341,"uid":366401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T18:23:50.000Z","msg":"又冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27df13b28d47685e54665e6c0d32138863d1ff9d","tid":2223341,"uid":71977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":